{"tid":563700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我活在連登的世界裡","createTime":"2018-02-17T07:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-17T08:00:45.000Z","uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"53a26fbdebfd9028a0dca46cf3730cbda1dbf977","tid":563700,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"同啲fd傾計<br />\n有時講下啲金句<br />\n點知冇一個聽得明 <br />\n唔知個金句代表啲咩事 有咩意思<br />\n仲要畀佢地笑返轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就好似傾傾下計 佢地講笑咁講話 <br />\n要開分身同自己傾計<br />\n咁我一諗就諗到：<br />\n尋晚kelly鬧得我好岩（啱）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點知佢地咁都聽唔撚明 明明單野咁經典<br />\n就算我冇上高登連登 fb都有見過人分享出嚟<br />\n<br />\n跟住有個朋友話想買嘢<br />\n於是我又講：<br />\n不如加多少少 上___<br />\n諗住講下笑<br />\n點知又冇人睇得明<br />\n又變咗恥笑對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e2f36dcd888fa83901cdaa8a7de3867983e4f0","tid":563700,"uid":40804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:51:09.000Z","msg":"沒有一點點防備"},{"pid":"7140acd3bfe5b96b6974111f439f92b1a2d58e44","tid":563700,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:51:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"71cbfe285c3988cc19f94eb01ecc33fe8c2ba0b3","tid":563700,"uid":92459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"你講乜鳩"},{"pid":"0820d9f776549d0d1d12de31a08b207cb78d24c8","tid":563700,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:51:47.000Z","msg":"好型 好想識你牙"},{"pid":"5cd94d613e17e08476c68b0d3981d4e1dd3f4254","tid":563700,"uid":171598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-17T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/17/155309_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fuploa